Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是从你们的面前消失罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被跟踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就只是时间早晚的问题罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万事皆休了吗？
