Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.05,0:18:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们最后怎样了？
