Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里才是现实的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
